nts, are more pronounced in dwarfs since they more vulnerable to the\neffects of strangulation and harassment than giant galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Dec 2006 21:02:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
